 (*) added support since last slave release)
 
 version 2.3 (19.05.2024) done by JOTD:
 - fixed bug that crashed the game when tactic is changed/loaded (issue #0006185). The bug
   is there since the first version of the slave, but somehow hidden below
   another bug which also made tactics not useable.
 - england teams are now selectable again
 - game now looks in "data" directory for files, just like the installer copies them.
   so you can move back the files into a "data" folder, if you didn't fix that with
   a "data" tooltype already.

 version 2.2 (07.06.2023) done by JOTD:
 - reworked file load/save completely (which fixed load/save tactic bug)
 - highlights/seasons/leagues/careers are loaded/saved in "save" directory
 - allows to load big team.xxx files (requires 256k more memory)
 - fixed install script
 - workaround for random access fault when selecting teams (not systematic)
 
 version 2.1 (09.05.2021) done by JOTD:
 - german version supported (issue #0002640)
 
 version 2.0 (06.05.2021) done by JOTD:
 - fixed long time slowdown issue by making the game use fastmem
   (issue #0000003)
 - fixed memory requirements to use only 1MB chip (issue #0002283)
 - quit key on 68000 machines (except for 1994 v0.9 version)
 - snoop bugs removed (except for 1994 v0.9 version)
 - reworked source code
 - reworked readme file
 - source code included
 
 version 1.x (2001) done by Galahad:
 - initial release
 - Full load from Hard drive (REAL files)
 - Lame-o-Protect removed (Copylock)/(2x Copylock in versions 1.52)
 - Load/Save Seasons/Tactics/Leagues/Careers/Highlights/Diy to Hard Drive
 - Memory bus error fixed!
 - Bus error fixed! (Highlights)
 - CACR code removed
 - Divide by Zero code removed
 - RomIcon, NewIcon (x2) and GlowIcon (also x2) (all created by Frank!)
 - Quit option is 'Del'

 
 
